      <title>供过于求的前景盖过对中国刺激措施的乐观情绪，导致油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对即将出现的供应过剩的持续担忧掩盖了明年中国采取更大胆刺激措施的前景，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 23:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
